Dad.

40
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:50,950
They killed my sister.

41
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,899
They killed my sister.

42
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:54,470
I will make them pay.

43
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:55,539
I will avenge her.

44
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:57,499
All right.

45
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:58,619
Don't worry.

46
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:01,350
Yuling, I'm here.

47
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:03,419
I will avenge your sister.

48
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:04,550
Trust me.

49
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,710
Once we've settled everything,

50
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,830
let's bring
her favourite lilies, all right?

51
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:13,670
Okay.

52
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:14,790
Okay.

53
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:16,030
Good girl.

54
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:17,710
That's my girl.

55
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:33,859
I asked the florist
to add some sunflowers.

56
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:35,590
They'll brighten your mood a little.

57
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:39,539
You've been exhausted
from training lately.

58
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:41,310
Take this chance to get some rest.

59
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:52,310
The weather is great today.

60
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,750
Want to go for a walk?

61
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:56,299
Sure.

62
00:02:56,300 --> 00:02:57,670
Let's go. I'll go with you.

63
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:06,510
Are you crazy?

64
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:07,659
Do you have any idea

65
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:09,859
how sensitive
the Mu Chenxi case is right now?

66
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,950
And you still spoke
to the reporters like that?

67
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,190
I only told the truth.

68
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:16,710
The truth?

69
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:19,590
You've been in this industry for years.
Haven't you realised yet?

70
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,019
No one cares

71
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,510
whether what you say is true or not.

72
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,419
Making a statement means taking a side.

73
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:27,739
I worked so hard to resolve that whole
"longing for your first love" mess.

74
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:29,910
And now
you're jumping into another scandal?

75
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,670
Chen Zhiqing.

76
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,990
Where's your ambition?

77
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:36,099
What happened to the person
who stood outside the company doors,

78
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:38,630
swearing to become
the biggest star in Huanxi?

79
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:41,510
Is a woman really worth all this?

80
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:59,059
I know I can play that role well.

81
00:03:59,060 --> 00:04:00,579
If you give me this chance,

82
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,459
I promise...

83
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,699
I will become

84
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,670
the top star in Huanxi.

85
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:13,110
I'm just tired of showing the same face.

86
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,750
Is that so wrong?

87
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,470
Chairman.

88
