The initial investment was huge

89
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:36,270
for project "Misaligned Lovers".

90
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:38,550
If it doesn't proceed smoothly,

91
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:40,200
the company will suffer great losses.

92
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:42,299
With the scandal
surrounding Mu Chenxi and Zhao Qian,

93
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,990
