94
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:46,990
For the sake of the project,
we may have to replace her.

95
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:51,750
However...

96
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:53,670
Mr. Yan

97
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:55,590
