98
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:12,630
Ms. Lin.

99
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:13,739
Yan Lidong isn't here.

100
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:14,950
Please come back another time.

101
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:19,550
I'm here to see you.

102
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,070
Mr. Fan came to see me.

103
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:25,750
He said the company wants to replace
the female lead in "Misaligned Lovers".

104
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:30,219
From the company's perspective,

105
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:31,270
I understand.

106
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:36,270
Is this still the Mu Chenxi
I used to know?

107
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:42,299
At a time like this,

108
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:45,430
