119
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:33,350
Mr. Fan.

120
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:37,390
Regarding "Misaligned Lovers",
what did the chairman say?

121
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,990
Follow Mr. Yan's decision.

122
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,859
And if the other
board members question it?

123
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:46,030
I'll handle it.

124
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:53,819
So you're saying,

125
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:55,830
